   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Provide Relief for Syrian Refugees</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Over 4 million Syrians have fled the civil war in their country for the relative safety of neighboring countries. The flow of refugees into camps and host communities continues to swell - far beyond initial expectations - and strain limited resources in the region. Mercy Corps is helping refugees and community members in Jordan, Lebanon, Iraq and within Syria by providing essentials like clothing and blankets, digging wells and building safe places for children to play and be kids.</narrative>
